# Build Skill

Build **{{PROJECT_NAME}}** using **{{BUNDLER}}**.

## Usage

```sh
{{BUNDLER}} build
```

## Common commands

| Task | Command |
|------|---------|
| Development build | `{{BUNDLER}} build` |
| Production build | `{{BUNDLER}} build --mode production` |
| Watch mode | `{{BUNDLER}} build --watch` |
| Clean | Remove `dist/` or `build/` output directory |

## Output

Build artifacts are written to the `dist/` or `build/` directory.

## Notes

- Run `{{LINTER}}` before building to catch issues early
- Production builds should always pass `{{TEST_RUNNER}}` before deployment
